309
00:18:42,440 --> 00:18:43,930
someone so easy

310
00:18:44,030 --> 00:18:45,310
to take down.

311
00:19:01,160 --> 00:19:02,020
Your Highness,

312
00:19:02,110 --> 00:19:03,910
