340
00:23:57,990 --> 00:24:00,360
[Memorial Tablet of My Late Son,
Zhuang Jingheng]

341
00:24:01,070 --> 00:24:01,680
Jingheng,

342
00:24:02,670 --> 00:24:04,910
[Memorial Tablet of My Late Son,
Zhuang Jingheng]

343
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:04,070
what I promised you

344
00:24:04,070 --> 00:24:05,330
