00:29:55,400 --> 00:29:56,350
Let me out!

433
00:29:56,500 --> 00:29:58,070
Let me out!

434
00:29:58,270 --> 00:29:59,400
Is anyone there?

435
00:29:59,750 --> 00:30:01,680
