00:30:37,830 --> 00:30:38,960
When did you get in?

440
00:30:42,790 --> 00:30:43,760
What do you want?

441
00:30:43,960 --> 00:30:44,880
Let me out now.

442
00:30:47,070 --> 00:30:48,270
I have never seen

443
00:30:48,680 --> 00:30:50,400
