444
00:30:51,400 --> 00:30:52,590
I had you brought here

445
00:30:52,590 --> 00:30:53,310
just to see

446
00:30:53,310 --> 00:30:54,710
Xia Jingshi's reaction.

447
00:30:56,680 --> 00:30:57,510
But sadly,

448
00:30:58,030 --> 00:30:58,680
he doesn't

449
00:30:59,110 --> 00:31:00,480
