494
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:56,170
How dare you…

495
00:33:09,920 --> 00:33:10,720
Interesting.

496
00:33:12,640 --> 00:33:13,640
In my entire life,

497
00:33:14,590 --> 00:33:16,190
